# ─── Generated code ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# gen/ and internal/db/sqlcgen/ are intentionally committed.
# Committed generated code enables reproducible `go build` without buf/sqlc.
# Regenerate with `make generate` after editing proto or SQL files.

